<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 18:19:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国际象棋-卡尔森与国际棋联关于自由式世界锦标赛的争论愈演愈烈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/chess-carlsen-v-fide-row-intensifies-over-freestyle-world-championship-2025-01-21/</link><description>国际象棋联合会（FIDE）与马格努斯·卡尔森之间持续不断的争端升级，该管理机构周二对自由式国际象棋棋手俱乐部进行了猛烈攻击，威胁要采取法律行动。自由式棋手俱乐部由这位挪威伟人共同拥有。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 16:18:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/chess-carlsen-v-fide-row-intensifies-over-freestyle-world-championship-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国副总理与戴蒙、苏世民和其他达沃斯金融家共进午餐</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-vice-premier-lunches-with-dimon-schwarzman-other-davos-financiers-2025-01-21/</link><description>周二，中国国务院副总理丁薛祥在达沃斯举行的私人午餐会上会见了全球金融和商界领袖，包括黑石集团首席执行官史蒂夫·施瓦茨曼(Steve Schwarzman)、桥水基金创始人雷·达里奥(Ray Dalio)和摩根大通首席执行官杰米·戴蒙(Jamie Dimon)。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-vice-premier-lunches-with-dimon-schwarzman-other-davos-financiers-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>尽管特朗普推迟禁令，TikTok应用程序仍无法在美国苹果和谷歌商店上使用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-app-unavailable-apple-google-stores-us-despite-trump-delaying-ban-2025-01-21/</link><description>周二，TikTok 在美国的苹果和谷歌应用商店中仍然无法使用，一天前，唐纳德·特朗普总统签署了一项行政命令，将对这款流行的中国短视频应用程序的禁令的执行推迟 75 天。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:08:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-app-unavailable-apple-google-stores-us-despite-trump-delaying-ban-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>副总理表示中国不追求贸易顺差</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-is-not-seeking-trade-surplus-vice-premier-says-2025-01-21/</link><description>中国副总理丁薛祥周二表示，中国不追求贸易顺差，愿意进口更有竞争力的优质产品和服务来平衡贸易。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 13:27:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-is-not-seeking-trade-surplus-vice-premier-says-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>2024年中国非金融类对外直接投资同比增长10.5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-2024-non-financial-outbound-direct-investment-rose-105-year-2025-01-21/</link><description>中国商务部周二表示，按美元计算，2024年中国非金融类对外直接投资同比增长10.5%，达到1439亿美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 12:25:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-2024-non-financial-outbound-direct-investment-rose-105-year-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>四国外长在华盛顿举行会议，表明特朗普对中国的关注</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/quad-foreign-ministers-meet-washington-signal-trumps-china-focus-2025-01-21/</link><description>美国国务卿卢比奥表示，周二在华盛顿与澳大利亚、印度和日本同行举行的会议将强调与盟友“在对美国和美国人重要的事情上”合作的重要性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 12:04:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/quad-foreign-ministers-meet-washington-signal-trumps-china-focus-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>副总理表示中国不追求贸易顺差愿平衡贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-stable-growth-strong-impetus-global-economy-vice-premier-says-2025-01-21/</link><description>中国副总理丁薛祥周二表示，中国不追求贸易顺差，愿意进口更有竞争力的优质产品和服务来平衡贸易。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 11:17:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-stable-growth-strong-impetus-global-economy-vice-premier-says-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：“走走停停”特朗普关税贸易鞭打美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-21/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 11:07:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>中缅泰达成铲除电信诈骗中心共识</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-myanmar-thailand-reach-consensus-eradicate-telecom-fraud-centres-2025-01-21/</link><description>据中国国家广播电台报道，中国、缅甸、泰国官员周二在中国昆明举行会议，就消除缅甸电信诈骗中心达成共识。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 10:47:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-myanmar-thailand-reach-consensus-eradicate-telecom-fraud-centres-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>万科困境考验中国房地产业复苏努力的极限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/vanke-woes-test-limits-chinas-property-sector-revival-efforts-2025-01-21/</link><description>近年来，在采取了多项措施解决房地产市场的流动性危机之后，预计北京最终将重拾旧的做法，直接介入以稳定被视为该行业领头羊的国有开发商。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 10:33:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/vanke-woes-test-limits-chinas-property-sector-revival-efforts-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲向美国伸出援手，警告“竞相触底”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/eus-von-der-leyen-says-need-work-together-avoid-global-race-bottom-2025-01-21/</link><description>特朗普表示，他希望扭转美国对欧盟的贸易逆差。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 10:13:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/eus-von-der-leyen-says-need-work-together-avoid-global-race-bottom-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>报告称，中国奢侈品市场进入“新常态”，预计 2025 年销量持平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-enters-new-normal-luxury-market-with-flat-sales-expected-2025-report-says-2025-01-21/</link><description>咨询公司贝恩公司在发布最新《中国奢侈品报告》时表示，2024年中国奢侈品市场将下降18%至20%，标志着“指数增长”时期的结束，预计今年销售额将保持平稳周二。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:53:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-enters-new-normal-luxury-market-with-flat-sales-expected-2025-report-says-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>泰国对中国游客免签政策因一系列犯罪行为而受到批评</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailands-visa-waiver-chinese-tourists-under-fire-after-string-crimes-2025-01-21/</link><description>在备受瞩目的中国演员绑架案和类似犯罪事件引发人们对旅游业和安全的担忧之后，泰国对中国公民的免签证计划受到了密切关注。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:51:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailands-visa-waiver-chinese-tourists-under-fire-after-string-crimes-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>习近平和普京讨论与特朗普、乌克兰和台湾的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-vows-further-develop-ties-with-xi-just-hours-after-trump-inauguration-2025-01-21/</link><description>弗拉基米尔·普京和习近平拥有广阔的世界观，认为随着中国在许多领域挑战美国的霸主地位，西方已经颓废和衰落。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:49:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-vows-further-develop-ties-with-xi-just-hours-after-trump-inauguration-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>德国汽车协会呼吁“经济实力”应对特朗普</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-auto-association-calls-economic-strength-face-trump-2025-01-21/</link><description>德国汽车协会主席周二表示，德国和欧洲需要变得更加独立和更具竞争力，以应对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普提出的挑战。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:47:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-auto-association-calls-economic-strength-face-trump-2025-01-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>